data.description: ***Motivated Seller***  Welcome to this lovely colonial style home located on the eastern shore less than 5 miles from Route 50,  Chesapeake community college and approximately 8 miles from historic Centerville. This wonderful home sits on 6 acres of land, which includes a detached shed and barn located to the rear of the property. As you drive down the gravel driveway you will set eyes on a lovely 4 bedroom 4 bath colonial style home which includes 3 levels of wood beamed ceilings, multiple level patios, a dine in kitchen with cherry cabinetry and stainless steel appliances. As you step out onto one of the patios you will have beautiful views  of the rear of the property and beyond that. This property is located less than two hours away from Ocean City MD and less than an hour and a half from Washington Dc.
